orderDirections5.order: The parties must consider settling this litigation by any means of Alternative Dispute Resolution including Mediation

orderDirections6.order: The parties must file with the court and exchange skeleton arguments at least three days before the trial,       preferably by email if that is possible

orderDirections7.order: Oral evidence will not be permitted at the hearing from a witness whose statement has not been served       in accordance with this order or has been served late, except with permission from the Court
